text: "\n <div id=\"moduleIndex\">\n  # Slot Machine\n  We are going to make a slot\
  \ machine.\n  The slot machine we are going to make, will look a little like the\
  \ middle row on this image:\n  First, find 3 images for the slot machine to display,\
  \ e.g. cherry, orange, lime.\n\n            Each \"reel\" of the slot machine will\
  \ randomly display one of 3 images you have chosen (you can add more images later\
  \ if there is time).\n\n\n\n    Put a \"SPIN\" button onto the frame that causes\
  \ each of the 3 \"reels\" to randomly change the image they are showing.\n\n\n \
  \   If all 3 reels have the same image showing (like in the picture above), the\
  \ player wins. Display a \"YOU WIN\" message, optionally add a sound of success,\
  \ and if you are still having fun - update a win counter to show the user how many\
  \ times they have won.\n\n\n    You may find the code below helpful:\n\n\nprivate\
  \ JLabel createLabelImage(String fileName) throws MalformedURLException{\n     \
  \   URL imageURL = getClass().getResource(fileName);\n\tif (imageURL == null){\n\
  \t\tSystem.err.println(\"Could not find image \" + fileName);\n\t\treturn new JLabel();\n\
  \t}\n\tIcon icon = new ImageIcon(imageURL);\n\tJLabel imageLabel = new JLabel(icon);\n\
  \treturn imageLabel;\n}\n </div>\n\n"
